(May 25, 1955.)

Gertrude Bell, as Administratrix of the Estate of James Bell, Deceased, Appellant, v. City of New York, Respondent.

Judgment unanimously affirmed, with costs to the respondent.. No opinion. Concur — Peck, P. J., Cohn, Bastow and Botein, JJ. [See ante, p. 1140.]
